data.description: THIS IS IT! Luxurious 3 bed, 2.5 bath on the top 2 floors and 1 bed, 1bath in-law suite for the lower level. Fully renovated row home close to the Union Market district. The home features many architectural details & high end finishes including a gourmet kitchen with Island, stainless steel appliances, modern cabinetry, crown molding trim throughout, granite countertop and hardwood floor throughout! The skylights on the upper level make for lots of natural light. There's even a deck off the master bedroom. The lower level is rented though March. There is a front and back entrance to the lower level unit. Why not have part of your mortgage paid?! Large backyard with an electric roll down garage door that secures the open parking spot and the house. YOU GOT TO SEE IT FOR YOURSELF!
